lw_vb_fit_doc: Documentation of lw and vb predictions

lw_predictions.Rd

Contains log-log length-weight regression estimates for the top species of each survey group, separated by sex.

Usage

lw_predictions

Format

A data frame with 8444 rows and 9 variables:

fit_length

fish lengths

fit_weight

predicted weight at length

sex

sex, M or F

a

Scaling coefficient, intercept of length-weight regression

b

exponent, slope of length-weight regression

region

science center of data collection

common_name

common species name

survey

survey within region

scientific_name

scientific species name
